# 此文件展示 Python 代码对每个字段规则的【实际生成结果】
# 编写 Schema 时，对照此文件确保描述与实际输出一致

## 1.01 获取网关Token

### reqData (GET请求，无reqData)

### 实际返回
```json
{
  "responseCode": "0",
  "responseMsg": "成功",
  "accessToken": "A3F8E2C1D4B7E9F6A2C8D1E5F7B4A3C9",
  "expireTime": 1743568234000
}
```
- accessToken 是 32 位十六进制随机字符串（每次调用不同）
- expireTime 是当前毫秒时间戳 + 15分钟（固定未来时间）
- is_ref=true 时：此值会自动存入 state，下次接口可用 state:accessToken 取到

---

## 1.03 授权协议查询

### reqData 内部字段（由 nested:queryAgreement_req 生成）
```json
{
  "productCode": "qyloan",
  "grantType": "7",
  "identityCard": "110105199312251248",
  "mobileNumber": "13800138100",
  "name": "张伟"
}
```

### 实际返回
```json
{
  "responseCode": "000000",
  "signType": "SM3",
  "responseMsg": "成功",
  "data": {
    "list": [
      {
        "sceneCode": "SCENE_001",
        "forceRead": "1",
        "forceBottom": "1",
        "forceDuration": "30",
        "grantType": "01",
        "grantName": "个人信息采集",
        "title": "个人信息授权书",
        "content": "请确认您的授权信息，同意以上条款并签署。",
        "basePolicyId": "POLICY_10001",
        "version": "1.0"
      }
    ]
  }
}
```
- array:agreementItem 默认生成 1 个元素（随机 1-3 个）
- 实际返回中的 grantType 值是从 enum:01,02,07,08 中随机选一个

---

## 1.04 授权协议提交

### reqData 内部字段（nested:signAgreement_req + array:nodeList_item）
```json
{
  "productCode": "qyloan",
  "identityCard": "320105198805151327",
  "mobileNumber": "15900008211",
  "grantType": "1",
  "nodeList": [
    {
      "grantTypeItem": "7",
      "startTime": "2026-04-02 14:30:25",
      "endTime": "2026-04-15 23:59:59",
      "sceneCode": "SCENE_001"
    }
  ]
}
```

### 实际返回
```json
{
  "responseCode": "000000",
  "responseMsg": "成功",
  "data": {
    "grantAuthId": "20260402000001"
  }
}
```
- sequence:grantAuthId 生成日期+6位序号
- is_ref=true：此 grantAuthId 会被存入 state，后续接口 state:grantAuthId 可取到

