## 1.05 提交线索信息

### reqData 内部字段（nested:loanApplyCreate_req）
```json
{
  "apply_no": "20260402000002",
  "cust_name": "李娜",
  "id_card": "450300199001011234",
  "mobile": "13600136300",
  "car_license": "粤B5K8L2",
  "residence_province_code": "440000",
  "residence_province": "广东省",
  "residence_city_code": "440100",
  "residence_city": "广州市"
}
```

### 实际返回
```json
{
  "responseCode": "000000",
  "responseMsg": "成功",
  "data": {
    "out_apply_no": "20260402000003",
    "apply_no": "20260402000002"
  }
}
```
- apply_no：来自请求 body 中的值（body:apply_no）
- out_apply_no：自动生成的序号，每次调用自增

