## 1.07 断点查询

### reqData 内部字段（nested:queryClueStatus_req）
```json
{
  "mobileNumber": "13700137100",
  "orderId": "20260402000003",
  "clueNo": "20260402000003"
}
```

### 实际返回
```json
{
  "responseCode": "000000",
  "responseMsg": "成功",
  "data": {
    "status": "13",
    "url": "https://example.com/page?id=MOCK"
  }
}
```
- status：从 enum:01,13,20,21 中随机
- body:orderId 把请求 body 里的 orderId 原样返回

